com.nmoumoulidis.opensensor.restInterface
Class BatchDataSendToServerServiceHelper

java.lang.Object
  com.nmoumoulidis.opensensor.restInterface.BatchDataSendToServerServiceHelper

public class BatchDataSendToServerServiceHelper
extends java.lang.Object

The second key class that utilizes the phone as an data aggregator between the OpenSensor Station and Server. It is instantiated and used by the BatchDataRetrieveService to send the data that was retrieved from the OpenSensor Station and now are available on the phone, to the remote OpenSensor Server.

Author:
Nikos Moumoulidis
